data.description: Welcome to your forever home! This charming single-level brick residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and sits on a sprawling 6.67-acre wooded lot enveloped by picturesque trees and tranquil vistas. With the added bonus of a 1500 sq foot detached storage building/garage and NO home association fees, this property offers ample space and freedom. Inside, the interior has been freshly adorned with new luxury vinyl plank flooring and a coat of fresh paint. The home provides a spacious living room and a flexible room adjacent to the kitchen, ideal for either a family room or an office. The roomy kitchen shines with stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar and substantial pantry. Additionally, the property includes a convenient 2-car side-loading garage. The 1500 sq ft detached storage building features a sizable screened-in porch, an expansive garage space, and two extra storage bays. Situated close to HWY 22, this home offers quick access to area attractions, stores, restaurants, and the local beaches, making it a rare find. Don't miss this opportunity; call today to schedule your showing!
